<p>Set screening expressions in the conditions tab.</p><p>Example: To set out of quota if NOT Male (Ie survey is for Male only): Add a ShowIf condition, where you pick Gender question and set the option to Male and set the comparisson to !=.</p><p>Notice that when the expression evalutes to TRUE, the respondent is filtered OUT.</p><p>You can add multiple requirements within 1 showif condition, in which case you can choose between AND/OR, or use multiple showif conditions, in which case they are implicitly OR.</p><p>Due to the implicit OR, it is not necessary to delete the initial showif &quot;false&quot;.</p>

QUESTION CHECK_QUOTA PAGE
IF (checkAllQuotas())
[
	DUMMY = true;
	CG_SCRIPT = "setRPQStatus(RPQ_Status_QuotaFull);
gotoQuestion(\"Goto_Inform\");
";
]


END

